    "There are two major groups of IML: (1) model-specific approaches that use the knowledge of a certain interpretable model for understanding predictions, and (2) model-agnostic methods that assess the predictive response of DL model (Bai et al. 2022).",
    "Some of these methods have Page 29 of 36 102 already been implemented in MD field (Xie et al. 2023; Vandermause et al. 2020; Li et al. 2022).",
